    <p>Category A: <strong>Traditional verse</strong> (rhyming, maximum 80 lines).<br>
       Category B: <strong>Free verse (maximum 80 lines)</strong>.<br>
       Category C: <strong>Short story</strong> (maximum 2,000 words).</p>
  </li>
